{"tid":857402,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［公關好忙］YG又粉碎左中國13億人既玻璃心","createTime":"2018-10-11T05:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T12:46:28.000Z","uid":88491,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0166daa4a1c547dc2a0b64524a11526f2929c28e","tid":857402,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T05:24:04.000Z","msg":"YG楊賢碩《YG戰資》又作死了，中國地圖完全不準確， 還有一個環節是兩個韓國保鏢打扮成清朝人， 劇情里到中國來做節目，被警察抓了，兩個保鏢用中文說「我是豬&quot;」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/11/132257_3dc26f003ba94c24ac13575c120a1d2b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2F132257_3dc26f003ba94c24ac13575c120a1d2b.png&h=b6656a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/11/132259_d98123a67096a30d08406af43715c3dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2F132259_d98123a67096a30d08406af43715c3dd.png&h=1e98562a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/11/132259_d5e19408f1f2323042738f2e97bb1705.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2F132259_d5e19408f1f2323042738f2e97bb1705.png&h=0c1caa50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n繼上次捉Winner驗毒之後又有新野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb8acb1799458ffc3c228fdf6d0068044ad0022","tid":857402,"uid":52339,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T05:26:55.000Z","msg":"YG同中國人都係豬 冇講錯喎 打和啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b7b8ab93c9dffffdb5572389b116f723ac5db9","tid":857402,"uid":88491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T05:28:10.000Z","msg":"呢單我諗起之前朴寶劍比強國抵制單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n朴寶劍被指廣告辱華　內地網民籲實施禁韓令<br />\n<br />\n原因是朴寶劍約在半年前為韓國K-SWISS拍攝廣告，故事講述他與一位稱號為「萬里長城」的男子對奕兼鬥舞。在片中「萬里長城」身形矮胖戴着粗金鍊，舞步笨拙之餘，更被女伴掌摑，亦輸掉棋賽。由於萬里長城是中國獨有的文化象徵，不少內地網民在看過廣告後，質疑廣告有辱華之嫌！有評論直指這是「一邊賺錢還一邊諷刺，希望禁韓令早日實施」更得到不少內地網民的附和，亦有自稱朴寶劍的粉絲對他大呼失望。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1631ca39f73448a2fea8f43867393c73e905ee","tid":857402,"uid":80814,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T05:49:53.000Z","msg":"全球圍堵中國，要企啱陣營啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24cfb8281062ceeb0bb5df1a73f028f6cb8702b","tid":857402,"uid":88491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"feb8acb1799458ffc3c228fdf6d0068044ad0022","tid":857402,"uid":52339,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T05:26:55.000Z","msg":"YG同中國人都係豬 冇講錯喎 打和啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:05:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5477383a557e91be476e032a732aa53bdef14b","tid":857402,"uid":88491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/11/181723_8a95382316e9ddbb7c8ec2743bf54ce5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2F181723_8a95382316e9ddbb7c8ec2743bf54ce5.png&h=558adf06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abaeb053eddef5555f315a52c407652e782ce96","tid":857402,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e1631ca39f73448a2fea8f43867393c73e905ee","tid":857402,"uid":80814,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T05:49:53.000Z","msg":"全球圍堵中國，要企啱陣營啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2